### ========== COURSE TESTS ==========

### ✅ Student - Get All Courses (should 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

###

### ✅ Student - Get Course by ID (should 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

###

### ✅ Student - Search Courses (should 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/search?keyword=data
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

###

### ❌ Student - Create Course (should 403)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

{
    "course_code": "TEST05",
    "course_name": "Test Course",
    "credits": 3
}

###

### ✅ Instructor - Create Course (should 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

{
    "course_code": "TEST03",
    "course_name": "Test Course",
    "credits": 3
}

### ✅ Instructor - Delete Course (should 201)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/courses/4  
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{instructorToken}}

###

### ✅ Admin - Create Course (should 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/create   
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "course_code": "TEST04",
    "course_name": "Test Course",
    "credits": 3
}

### ✅ Admin - Delete Course (should 201)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}



